SELECT customer_id, feedback_text FROM feedback_data WHERE feedback_id IN (SELECT feedback_id FROM sentiment_analysis WHERE sentiment_score > 0.8);
SELECT rating, COUNT(*) AS count FROM feedback_data GROUP BY rating ORDER BY count DESC;
SELECT feedback_date, AVG(sentiment_score) AS avg_score FROM feedback_data JOIN sentiment_analysis ON feedback_data.feedback_id = sentiment_analysis.feedback_id GROUP BY feedback_date;

SELECT feedback_data.feedback_id, feedback_text, analysis_date, sentiment_score FROM feedback_data JOIN sentiment_analysis ON feedback_data.feedback_id = sentiment_analysis.feedback_id WHERE sentiment_score < 0.5 ORDER BY analysis_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT c.feedback_text, s.sentiment_label FROM CustomerFeedbacks c JOIN SentimentAnalysis s ON c.feedback_id = s.feedback_id WHERE s.sentiment_score > 0.8;

SELECT p.product_id, p.improvement_text, i.implementation_date FROM ProductImprovements p JOIN ProductImprovements i ON p.improvement_id = i.improvement_id WHERE i.implementation_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
